{"tid":1930974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以雕個林鄭跪地幫習近平含撚像？","createTime":"2020-03-18T02:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T02:34:16.000Z","uid":205884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f09f8f4a651d85583d71e811b33e9da4cc7a1d6","tid":1930974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z50095U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ50095U.png&h=168c5f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離post睇到呢幅圖<br />\n就好似習豬頭唔係得個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人肯搞我地一定要多多捐錢<br />\n呢個像可以考慮暫時放起大學裡面<br />\n他日香港重光就永久放置政總公園<br />\n壓住成個政府啲蝗氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxnbxkJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxnbxkJ.jpg&h=c1c0cb68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似南京岳飛廟既秦檜伉儷像咁<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要比人日夜屌老母吐口水先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算死咗九泉之下都要你不得安息</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c284ccf34acc64a129ccec0247b2be139176eb1e","tid":1930974,"uid":205884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:20:08.000Z","msg":"用藝術抗爭<br />\n發揮想像力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851b906057b4c1e983b8ab38df106349cb9e55bf","tid":1930974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:20:30.000Z","msg":"一推推 721"},{"pid":"e0b9e8ef965d2f46525bf4e2377266981a819739","tid":1930974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"再推推 831"},{"pid":"f3037188d83c5f24acbb8c2c655a20af53976aa5","tid":1930974,"uid":706,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"半年前我已經提議過幫班冚家產立個銅像，生生世世跪香港人"},{"pid":"fdc2a590cdb0e31166543c200f888b914405a55d","tid":1930974,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"